{"tid":148600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★FF 假如你係特首，有冇方法另樓價去返以下水平？","createTime":"2017-03-08T16:31:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T05:57:39.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9997f1cfa4313c9fb6637ebdc6181ec10f8fc507","tid":148600,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:31:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/22/180418_b358df40dd36a13778fca75e72da48ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F22%2F180418_b358df40dd36a13778fca75e72da48ef.jpg&h=b52ac344&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"196913de92aae8de5fff6f9e5bf9817487a78e44","tid":148600,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:31:33.000Z","msg":"有冇可能？"},{"pid":"c9c426b2bdaad7dbfdf0e423372a300e1e2cb56a","tid":148600,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:31:35.000Z","msg":"大鑊飯"},{"pid":"1ce5a29c4a6e519043940cc50d42244c5f966ec7","tid":148600,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:33:08.000Z","msg":"每個港人只可買一次樓，終生不能轉讓/售"},{"pid":"e8817bd86f4a9ef49cd6b516c91b14ea842fa76c","tid":148600,"uid":20256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:35:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每個港人只可買一次樓，終生不能轉讓/售</blockquote><br />\n公司名義？"},{"pid":"d2cf4085b42cd2d2b661204d016b9755e8ea72ce","tid":148600,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:37:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>每個港人只可買一次樓，終生不能轉讓/售</blockquote><br />\n公司名義？</blockquote><br />\none ID one chance<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"535d3458c11fbd0555ac33c09797879313f0e332","tid":148600,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:49:19.000Z","msg":"重提空置稅 講得出難做到？<br />\n2013年01月21日 星期一<br />\n<a href=\"http://paper.hket.com/article/79554/重提空置稅%20講得出難做到？\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaper.hket.com%2Farticle%2F79554%2F%E9%87%8D%E6%8F%90%E7%A9%BA%E7%BD%AE%E7%A8%85%2520%E8%AC%9B%E5%BE%97%E5%87%BA%E9%9B%A3%E5%81%9A%E5%88%B0%EF%BC%9F&d=L%2B62T2%2Bn9M6BECqB4mLSskkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=d9973f0e\" target=\"_blank\">paper.hket.com/article/79554/重提空置稅%20講得出難做到？</a><br />\n<br />\n&hellip;<br />\n其實，外國一般推行空置稅均不論一手或二手，甚至連度假屋也不放過，在英國市鎮Tamworth，月初便通過了打擊空置樓宇的加稅措施，若然房子空置逾2年，屋主日後要繳交地方政府稅，金額將提高一半，當地現時共有96間空置逾2年的房子。<br />\n<br />\n空置稅的空置定義一向最多爭拗，要找出空置單位也涉及行政成本，外國有些地方乾脆只容許居民擁有一個單位，若然超過一個，非經常居住的單位已會被視為「空置」。例如法國，除了自住的物業外，其他擁有的房產一律當作空置，空置一年便要徵收樓價10%稅款，空置兩年是12.5%，3年15%，即使發展商就算把空置單位賣給空殼公司，也逃不過空置稅。<br />\n<br />\n荷蘭政府對付空置房的手法更辣，若有房屋長期空置，容許其他市民入住，瑞典政府更有權徵用空置單位廉租予無樓家庭。如此辣招，令港人難以想像。<br />\n&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n方法唔係冇，睇下敢唔敢學。"},{"pid":"4dde89cd1779705596eaa4b04d1f748441ebf06d","tid":148600,"uid":70501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T17:15:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>每個港人只可買一次樓，終生不能轉讓/售</blockquote><br />\n公司名義？</blockquote><br />\none ID one chance<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n單程證30萬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf432464f93cc6391179695cba24faa0ac0cefc","tid":148600,"uid":60432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T17:23:55.000Z","msg":"爆次天災就可能得"},{"pid":"3a68fecaf9d2e378dfe8a96d7cb2e161ff4cae6b","tid":148600,"uid":13277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T17:25:15.000Z","msg":"八萬五"},{"pid":"143abd2d4ca671c4b82dfa0abb1f924a631fcd2a","tid":148600,"uid":2671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T17:34:55.000Z","msg":"投共"},{"pid":"1fa32f1ac5898e874a1739b9361a3bd093f0df81","tid":148600,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T18:17:51.000Z","msg":"其實學台灣咁<br />\n兩個物業時物業稅加倍增加<br />\n越多物業稅就越重<br />\n同時有豪宅加稅<br />\n總之無咩肉食咁<br />\n樓價自然回落"},{"pid":"ec870fbe33de319cb7e2b915cb9e2a2bc14b4103","tid":148600,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T18:20:44.000Z","msg":"揾返楊永強做香港衛生福利及食物局局長"},{"pid":"de46665faa007a5aee7c5e64a403f1e8c5c2624b","tid":148600,"uid":72020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T18:21:06.000Z","msg":"一日有人買 一人冇可能到03價"},{"pid":"58d7c28b556d68e73bfb270f91c193db761cdddc","tid":148600,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T02:00:25.000Z","msg":"組織休班警同藍絲攻打英美領事館"},{"pid":"3d77ed7de1ca1922cd7f1303ab0b2728f372b549","tid":148600,"uid":11719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T02:08:48.000Z","msg":"限制樓價，限制單位數量，然後降低地價，另地產商唔可以謀取暴利，禁止起豪宅/會所，只准賣俾身份證有三粒人仕"},{"pid":"233395502c1bedd1c228244032ac53c54972414c","tid":148600,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T02:09:59.000Z","msg":"唔顧住班小業主狂打，到時唔洗買啦，有命自己行入去住啦。如果3，2年內樓價斬一半，好多人跳樓都唔掂。最理想就係市區重建 唔準起豪宅，起返d正常既住宅，新盤唔爆起，個市場就慢慢下調"},{"pid":"509df7ae7d708cc3a446c698b9c869c1753a10a4","tid":148600,"uid":10503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T02:10:14.000Z","msg":"第二層樓俾80%印花稅"},{"pid":"3064b15b7a74f0f0b0db24375ff4670bd8d3ac77","tid":148600,"uid":49955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T02:13:38.000Z","msg":"賣地係政府主要收入來源<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n哩個先係問題既本身"},{"pid":"e3e4aef3653f434aa9b8b6b3c82c8b67b73f5f38","tid":148600,"uid":2450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T02:18:48.000Z","msg":"折關口，解放香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"957062f43972d6ffe29cc74fe8638b29b84d1018","tid":148600,"uid":82935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T02:19:18.000Z","msg":"一定要CUT 左 150單程證 <br />\n<br />\n再&quot;配合&quot;鄰國中国打貪 及打走資., <br />\n將所有中国官員富豪在港資產充公.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/fa